{"tid":2233753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3 旺角藥房員工確診　傳曾到 China Secret 慶中秋","createTime":"2020-10-07T11:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T12:12:53.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6a54b8c75909587b0adf3a4a2d732a97d5f90a5c","tid":2233753,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"另外亦有 3 名確診者分別在旺角 3 間藥房工作，分別是 38 歲男子 (#5136), 43 歲男子 (#5135) 及 37 歲男子 (#5137)，三人分別在豉油街大華藥房、西洋菜南街龍城中西大藥房及亞皆老街龍城中西藥房工作。張竹君表示，3 人之間有交流，會「借貨、傾計」。3 人分別在 10 月 3 日及 4 日開始感不適，於 10 月 5 日早上各自到養和醫院求醫。3 人中以 43 歲男子最先發病，相信是 3 人間的源頭，但他的感染源頭亦未明。<br />\n<br />\n有記者則提出，收到消息旺角多間藥房員工，曾一起到 China Secret 慶中秋，張竹君則指「收到你哋報料」，已請警方協助調查，但暫時未有資料。<br />\n<br />\n至於殘疾院舍院友則是一名 57 歲男子 (#5140)，住在葵涌國寶之家，亦有另兩名院友初步確診。《立場》則接獲消息，指再有 9 宗確診完成覆檢，將在翌日公布<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaad1f3059ec843b68e7b6709f51cd29b6b6182","tid":2233753,"uid":159313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"酒吧群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bc0d6bf73c25c37b88618c8099c79c9f8dcc75","tid":2233753,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"成班芝麻人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8f8eb4338500264dee7a99507732893062ce26","tid":2233753,"uid":118520,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"確診流感都係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19183cb08ddeac9093e2879153ad276c64936da","tid":2233753,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90ec208b54ea20261b38988c4ef51ed0ba378a0","tid":2233